The municipality will pay this supplier, which has been monitored by the Supreme Audit Office for selling at high prices, another fine.
What hasn't been said is the total amount the city council still owes her and how many checks will be sent to Camach Palazuelos.
"Nothing has been bought now, only what we owe her is being paid, as are other suppliers", he said in an interview.
